These are Puzzles for 1x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-2-1::.
There are 3 different nationalities: chinese, russian, nigerian
1. the nigerian is on the left of the russian##1
2. the nigerian is between the chinese and the russian##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |  2   |    3     |
| Nationality   | chinese | nigerian | russian |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-2-2::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: crime, animation, drama
1. the person watching crime movies is between the person watching animation movies and the person watching drama movies##2
2. the person watching animation movies is on the right of the person watching crime movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |   3    |
| Movie-Genre   | drama | crime | animation |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-2-3::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: funk, pop, soul
1. the fan of pop is between the fan of funk and the fan of soul##2
2. the fan of pop is on the left of the fan of funk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |  2   |    3    |
| Music-Genre   | soul | pop | funk |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-2-4::.
3 different pets are kept: mouse, fish, dog
1. the owner of the dog is on the left of the owner of the fish##1
2. the owner of the dog is between the owner of the fish and the owner of the mouse##2

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1    |   2   |     3      |
| Pet   | mouse | dog | fish |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-2-5::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, mirinda, lemonade
1. the person drinking almond-milk is between the person drinking lemonade and the person drinking mirinda##2
2. the person drinking lemonade is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |  2   |  3   |
| Beverage   | mirinda | almond-milk | lemonade |

 #################################

 
